---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SchemaMarkup from "../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("October 26 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

---

<BaseLayout
  title="Ultimate Pre-Party Cleaning Checklist | Valley Clean Team"
  description={isPublished ? "Full Article: The Ultimate Pre-Party Cleaning Checklist" : "Coming Soon: The Ultimate Pre-Party Cleaning Checklist"}
  noindex={!isPublished}
  ogImage="https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/iKQIBhpKVL2XVPgU7HMd/media/6920802945dc047d65b4ec5d.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="The Ultimate Pre-Party Cleaning Checklist"
    description="Hosting a party? Follow our ultimate pre-party cleaning checklist to ensure your home looks spectacular and welcoming for all your guests."
    publishDate="October 26 2026"
    author={author}
  />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Hosting
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          The Ultimate Pre-Party Cleaning Checklist
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming October 26 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>October 26 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <!-- TODO: REPLACE THIS SECTION WITH YOUR ACTUAL BLOG CONTENT -->
          <h2>What is the Ultimate Pre-Party Cleaning Checklist?</h2>
<p><strong>The ultimate pre-party cleaning checklist is a systematic guide designed to ensure your home in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas is party-ready with military precision.</strong> It covers essential cleaning tasks that guarantee a welcoming atmosphere for your guests and help you host with confidence. Follow our expert guide to make your home the perfect venue for entertaining.</p>

<h3>Why a Pre-Party Cleaning Checklist Matters</h3>
<p>Hosting a party is a joyous occasion, but it comes with its share of stress. A well-organized cleaning checklist helps alleviate anxiety by providing a clear path to readiness. Our checklist ensures that every corner of your home is pristine, giving you peace of mind to focus on what truly matters: enjoying your event.</p>

<h4>Step-by-Step Pre-Party Cleaning Guide</h4>

<h4>1. Entryway Excellence</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Clear Clutter:</strong> Remove shoes, coats, and any miscellaneous items.</li>
  <li><strong>Spotless Surfaces:</strong> Wipe down doors and handles to create a welcoming first impression.</li>
  <li><strong>Floor Focus:</strong> Vacuum or mop entryway floors for a pristine appearance.</li>
</ul>

<h4>2. Living Room Luster</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Dust & Shine:</strong> Dust all surfaces, including shelves and electronics, for a polished look.</li>
  <li><strong>Seating Arrangement:</strong> Vacuum upholstery and fluff pillows for maximum comfort.</li>
  <li><strong>Decor Delight:</strong> Arrange decor to enhance the ambiance without cluttering.</li>
</ul>

<h4>3. Kitchen Cleanliness</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Counter Clarity:</strong> Clear and sanitize countertops to ensure a clean prep area.</li>
  <li><strong>Appliance Attention:</strong> Wipe down appliances, especially those in view, for a spotless shine.</li>
  <li><strong>Floor Freshness:</strong> Sweep and mop to eliminate any lingering crumbs or spills.</li>
</ul>

<h4>4. Bathroom Brilliance</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Mirror Magic:</strong> Clean mirrors for a streak-free reflection.</li>
  <li><strong>Sink & Surface Sanitation:</strong> Scrub sinks and wipe down surfaces for hygiene.</li>
  <li><strong>Guest-Ready Essentials:</strong> Stock fresh towels and toilet paper for convenience.</li>
</ul>

<h4>5. Dining Room Dazzle</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Table Tactics:</strong> Dust and polish the dining table for a gleaming finish.</li>
  <li><strong>Chair Care:</strong> Wipe down chairs, ensuring no dust or stains remain.</li>
  <li><strong>Lighting & Layout:</strong> Adjust lighting for a cozy ambiance and arrange seating for optimal flow.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Final Touches for a Perfect Party</h3>
<p>With your pre-party cleaning checklist completed, it's time to add the finishing touches. Ensure your home is well-ventilated with fresh air or scented candles. Set the mood with your preferred music playlist to keep energy high. Double-check all areas to ensure nothing has been overlooked.</p>

<h3>Reclaim Your Time with The Valley Clean Team</h3>
<p>Preparing for a party shouldn't be overwhelming. Let The Valley Clean Team handle the cleaning so you can focus on hosting. Our vetted specialists deliver guaranteed, precision cleaning in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas. <strong>Book today and reclaim your time—schedule your guaranteed service now!</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">October 26 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
</BaseLayout>
